steps.step:
In the style sheet, add this code to a new line:

        blockquote:before {
        color: #ccc;
        content: open-quote;
        font-size: 4em;
        line-height: 0.1em;
        margin-right: 0.20em;
        vertical-align: -0.4em;
        font-family: Arial;
        quotes: "\201C" "\201D";
        }

        blockquote:after {
        color: #ccc;
        content: close-quote;
        font-size: 4em;
        line-height: 0.1em;
        margin-left: 0.20em;
        vertical-align: -0.4em;
        font-family: Arial;
        quotes: "\201C" "\201D";
        }
